data.description: Beautiful home in Mustang, OK. 4 Bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with a 3 car garage. Great wood look tile and beautiful living room beam with a sleek gas log fireplace. Modern style, well maintained home. Granite/Quartz countertops with a lot of storage throughout! Backyard backs up to a green space. This home is great for entertaining! You'll want to check out the built in desk and mud bench! Don't miss out on this home! **LOAN IS ASSUMABLE FOR THOSE WHO QUALIFY**
